Class ModeratorPaginator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.paginators.Paginator<T>
      • net.dean.jraw.paginators.GenericPaginator<PublicContribution>
        • net.dean.jraw.paginators.ModeratorPaginator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Listing<PublicContribution>>, NetworkAccessible<RedditResponse,RedditClient>

    public class ModeratorPaginator
extends GenericPaginator<PublicContribution>
    This class provides a way to iterate over submissions and comments relevant to moderators, such as those reported and marked as spam.
